{"tid":1534520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有小小野想對何中既學生同家長們講","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:21.000Z","uid":269132,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d23ffe3ce98d0cc72b7979390c860fc2d9a304a","tid":1534520,"uid":269132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"老實講 讀何中既學生真係係一個無言論自由既學校讀書 , 我認為各家長不如幫你地子女轉校啦 , 有手足去聲援間垃圾學校就報警 琴日又一間課室放100多位學生軟禁 咁既學習環境真係好咩?<br />\n睇到有小手足被黑警撲倒地上 血流披面 痛心不已 <br />\n真心為左你地仔女好 齊齊轉校 反正岩岩開學 轉校為更好環境讀書 , 難道你地認為自己仔女連返學都無言論自由 點先會讀得好書 !?<br />\n<br />\nPS : 另外 其他學校既手足 你地只需全面杯葛狗2代就可以啦 唔需要同佢講半句野 或同狗2代有任何互動 全力報復係所有狗2代身上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b534add6485e49920d55d6e08f60774a03cd52b","tid":1534520,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-